snippet.title: MEAT SHIFT - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
It's time for your shift.

Meat Shift is a narrative game that takes place in the dirty halls of a  slaughterhouse and meat packing facility just after the turn of the 20th century. 

Content Warnings: Animal death, gore, blood.

Play the game now: https://rattusrattus.itch.io/meatshift

Follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/rattusrattusart

Check out our Gumroad with more game content: https://gumroad.com/rattusrattus

If you're craving even more Rat King, here's our website: https://ratkingcollective.weebly.com/
